Markup languages (a list is given as part of http://johnmacfarlane.net/pandoc/
  => SEE https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lightweight_markup_language
  * markdown: http://daringfireball.net/projects/markdown/
  * restructuredtext: http://docutils.sourceforge.net/docs/ref/rst/introduction.html
  * textile: http://redcloth.org/textile

Possible output:
  * HTML
  * Latex
  * PDF
  * OpenOffice/Word (RTF?)
